        <num>CC 885</num>
        <heading>885.  Basis of partition in cases of representation</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 885.  Basis of partition in cases of representation
In all cases in which representation is permitted, the partition is made
by roots; if one root has produced several branches, the subdivision is also
made by roots in each branch, and the members of the same branch take by
heads.</p>
        </content>
